    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>Consumed By Race</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Gwen Athene Tarbox letter disputes conclusions reached in July 16 issue that sorted out consumer habits by race.</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>What am I to make of the fact that more whites buy Cool Whip, but more blacks buy apple juice? This clumsy attempt to demystify blacks and whites to one another reminded me of how, when I was young, white friends who knew that I was close to many black people would ask, ''Do they have any furniture in their living rooms?''</p>
        <p>Gwen Athene Tarbox  Kalamazoo, Mich.</p>
      </block>
